## Data Attribution

This project uses data from the following sources:

- **USGS 3D Elevation Program (3DEP)** - Public Domain
- **USDA Forest Service** - Public Domain
- **COTREX (Colorado Trail Explorer)** - Colorado Parks and Wildlife
- **NOAA National Weather Service** - Public Domain
- **WeatherAPI.com** - API Services (requires attribution)
- **Esri/ArcGIS** - Base map tiles (attribution required)

Users of this software must maintain proper attribution for all data sources
as specified in the application and documentation.
